snippet.title: Sub Commander v1.22 (Flash game 200?)
snippet.description:
Sub Commander is a submarine game.
You have to navigate your sub to the finish line and avoid obstacles (rocky seabed, iceberg, floating mine, depth charge, enemy sub).
